For sphinxbase:

wget http://sourceforge.net/projects/cmusphinx/files/sphinxbase/0.6/sphinxbase-0.6.tar.gz/download


For sphinx3:

wget http://sourceforge.net/projects/cmusphinx/files/sphinx3/0.8/sphinx3-0.8.tar.gz/download

For sphinxtrain:

wget http://sourceforge.net/projects/cmusphinx/files/SphinxTrain/1.0/SphinxTrain-1.0.tar.bz2/download

-------------------------------------------

To Compile:

Sphinxbase:
------------

cd sphinxbase-0.6

./configure --prefix=/usr1/home/rsingh/mlsp_archive/sphinx.opensource.26may10

setenv PYTHONPATH /usr1/home/rsingh/mlsp_archive/sphinx.opensource.26may10/lib64/python2.5/site-packages/
mkdir -p ../lib64/python2.5/site-packages

make install


Sphinx3
-------

cd sphinx3-0.8
./configure --prefix=/usr1/home/rsingh/mlsp_archive/sphinx.opensource.26may10
make install

Sphinxtrain
-----------

cd SphinxTrain-1.0
./configure
make

